name: Sister
description:
Linda is the heroine of the film Gaspar Noe «Enter void», who combines beauty and lust. She has a life as a stripper, mindless sex, the death of her beloved brother and the disaster of her parents, it all affected her life. Behind all this is a «pretty face» and a great figure. So in my last job of three, a posh model contrasted with a faint blue color that doesn’t fit the beauty of the picture. 
That’s how the great director inspired me to create this triptych.
